aVThe only thing that they can't copy
p36
aVis the actual trademark label
p37
aVwithin that piece of apparel.
p38
aVThat's one reason that you see logos
p39
aVsplattered all over these products.
p40
aVIt's because it's a lot harder for knock-off artists
p41
aVto knock off these designs
p42
aVbecause they can't knock off the logo.
p43
aVBut if you go to Santee Alley, yeah.
p44
aV(Laughter) Well, yeah.
p45
